textTemplates.text:
The price includes the following: 1. Setup, configuration, and training 2. Updates and upgrades 3. Enhanced Support (see details here https://www.resilio.com/legal/support-plan/)

textTemplates.text:
The price includes the following: 1. Setup, configuration, and training 2. Updates and upgrades 3. API access 4. Enhanced Support (see details here https://www.resilio.com/legal/support-plan/) (Premium Support requires a minimum spend of $25,000/year.)
Available add-ons: 1. Object storage integration 2. Proxy 3. Distributed file locking 4. Caching
